com.picocontainer.gems.jndi

Class JNDIProvided<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.picocontainer.gems.jndi.JNDIProvided<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.picocontainer.ComponentAdapter<T>, Serializable

    public class JNDIProvided<T>
extends Object
implements com.picocontainer.ComponentAdapter<T>, Serializable
    Represents dependency provided via JNDI. This dependency is not to be managed by container at all, so there is no lifecycle, no monitoring etc.
    Author:
    Konstantin Pribluda
    See Also:
